					<h2>The NEXUS of Financial Power</h2>				
		<p>The name NEXA comes from the Latin nexus, meaning connection. To build on this, Jim Blackburn created the NEXA acronym—defining the core values of the types of elite financial professionals that we like to partner with:</p>		
					<h3>Featured Bios</h3>				
		<p>Visionaries Powering Your Process</p>		
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/1.png" alt="1 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/1.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/1-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/1-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Mike Kortas</h5>				
		<p>CEO of NEXA Mortgage</p>Mike Kortas, CEO and founder of NEXA Mortgage, has over 20 years of industry experience and has built NEXA into the largest mortgage broker in the U.S. since its launch in 2017. With 2,500+ loan officers across 48 states, his bold, disruptive leadership is driving rapid growth and innovation. Focused on doubling the company’s size by 2025, Kortas is reshaping the mortgage landscape with relentless ambition and a clear vision for market dominance.
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6A5FE5.png" alt="6A5Fe5 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6A5FE5.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6A5FE5-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6A5FE5-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Paul Adams
</h5>				
		<p>CIO of NEXA Mortgage</p>Paul Adams, CIO at NEXA Mortgage, brings 40+ years of IT leadership, overseeing strategy, innovation, and AI integration across NEXA and Jet NEXA. He ensures enterprise efficiency, security, and compliance through certified expertise in SOC and cybersecurity. Paul has led major infrastructure transformations, including for the U.S. Air Force, and founded Arizona Onsite Computer Services. His work consistently enhances operational resilience and drives competitive growth through cutting-edge technology.		
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2-2.png" alt="2 2 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2-2.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2-2-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/2-2-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Mike Neill
</h5>				
		<p>Director of NEXA Lending</p>With a proven track record in mortgage lending, I’ve helped grow a start-up to \$18M in revenue and earned recognition as a top producer by Mortgage Broker Magazine. As a Loan Officer and Recruiter at NEXA Mortgage, I’ve consistently achieved Presidents Club honors while mentoring others. I also serve as Chairman of the Board at Broker’s Care/NEXA Cares and have supported the Boys & Girls Club of the East Valley for over 30 years. Now, as Director of the Non-Delegated Correspondent division at NEXA, I focus on building strong teams and simplifying processes to drive collective success.		
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/3-1.png" alt="3 1 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/3-1.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/3-1-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/3-1-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Chris Porter
</h5>				
		<p>General Counsel of NEXA Mortgage</p>Christopher “Chris” Porter, General Counsel at NEXA Mortgage, oversees all legal affairs, providing strategic guidance to the executive team and managing litigation, regulatory matters, and business operations. With deep experience in financial services and the mortgage industry, he brings expertise in contract negotiation, risk management, and compliance, playing a key role in supporting NEXA’s growth and governance.
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/5-1.png" alt="5 1 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/5-1.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/5-1-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/5-1-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Dan Fouts
</h5>				
		<p>LOS Director of NEXA Mortgage</p>Dan Fouts began his career at NEXA Mortgage as a Loan Officer and quickly advanced to leadership, becoming Director of Loan Officer Support and NEXA University. He mentors loan officers across the company and leads training initiatives to enhance skills and drive performance. Through NEXA University, he curates educational webinars and resources that support loan officer growth and success nationwide. His leadership fosters a culture of collaboration and continued learning within NEXA.		
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/12.png" alt="12 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/12.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/12-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/12-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Rana Mortensenr
</h5>				
		<p>Executive Director of NEXA Mortgage</p>Rana serves as Executive Director at NEXA Mortgage, working closely with CEO Mike Kortas to drive the company’s strategic vision and support all departments. She founded “Women of NEXA” (WON) to empower women within the organization and the industry. Known for her integrity and drive, Rana is committed to fostering excellence and long-term success for NEXA and its partners.		
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6-1.png" alt="6 1 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6-1.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6-1-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/6-1-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
					<h5>Karen Enslin
</h5>				
		<p>BDM Director of NEXA Mortgage</p>With over 30 years in Real Estate and Finance, she began her career at NBT Bank and held roles at Navy Federal and Bank of America. Her passion for real estate led her to NEXA in 2020, where she now serves as Business Development Director for Corporate NEXA. In this role, she combines her coaching strengths and analytical skills to support growth across both industries.
															<img width="500" height="500" src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/11.png" alt="11 | Stairway Mortgage" srcset="/wp-content/uploads/2025/06/11.png 500w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/11-300x300.png 300w, /wp-content/uploads/2025/06/11-150x150.png 150w" sizes="(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px" />															
